28 and which pays or reimburses the person for the costs of the services or expenses.
29 Section 2 excludes certain arrangements for prepaid legal services from the definition of
30 legal expenses insurance. As such, under [this bill,] section 2, legal expenses insurance is
31 included among the various types of insurance that a casualty insurer may be authorized to
32 transact and subject to any applicable provision of existing law governing casualty insurance.
